nl.inl.blacklab.search.fimatch

Class ForwardIndexAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.inl.blacklab.search.fimatch.ForwardIndexAccessor

  • public abstract class ForwardIndexAccessor
extends Object
    Allows the forward index matching subsystem to access the forward indices, including an easy and fast way to read any annotation at any position from a document.
